# Copy to `.env` on the lab host and set Ollama to a reachable URL (loaded by Python via
# `modules/anna_training/repo_env.py` and by `scripts/anna_karpathy_loop_env.inc.sh`).
#
# Example when Ollama runs on another machine on the lab LAN:
# OLLAMA_BASE_URL=http://172.20.2.230:11434
#
# Default in code when unset is http://127.0.0.1:11434 — only works if ollama serve runs locally.
OLLAMA_BASE_URL=http://127.0.0.1:11434

# Optional — must exist in `ollama list` / /api/tags when using the LLM
# OLLAMA_MODEL=qwen2.5:7b

# Karpathy: default maps OBSERVATION_ONLY → CONDITION_TIGHTENING for execution_request wiring.
# Opt out of that (strict observational): ANNA_KARPATHY_DISABLE_LAB_WIRE_JACK=1
# Paper delegate after run_execution: real Jupiter Jack, or bundled stub.
# If BLACKBOX_JACK_EXECUTOR_CMD is unset, the harness uses scripts/runtime/jack_paper_bump_stub.py by default
# (tier-1 school completes the paper path). No bank settlement; paper_trades.jsonl is still what gates judge.
# Opt out with ANNA_KARPATHY_JACK_STUB=0.
# BLACKBOX_JACK_EXECUTOR_CMD=python3 scripts/runtime/jack_paper_bump_stub.py
# ANNA_KARPATHY_JACK_STUB=0
# Optional stub: JACK_STUB_ALWAYS_WIN=1 → always won + $0 when result unset (smoke tests). Deprecated: JACK_STUB_SIMULATE=0
# If every logged trade is won+$0, the Grade-12 numeric gate will NOT PASS (vacuous cohort). Dev override: ANNA_GRADE12_IGNORE_VACUOUS_WIN_STREAK=1
